<page-banner bg-image="../../img/bgs/edesign-bg.png"></page-banner>

<section id="ed">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <h1>about</h1>
    <h3>E-Design<span class="end-border">  _______</span></h3>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12">
          <h3 class="black">Franklin St</h3>
          <h6 class="black padded-bottom">Residential Design</h6>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
         <h5 class="img-desc">Inspiration</h5>
        <img src="/img/e-design/mood-board.png" class="img-responsive padded-bottom" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 text">
          <p>Ready for something new?  Our E-design program will allow you to connect with us remotely to complete a quick and fun design of your space.  With the information we’ve collected from your questionnaire, dimensions, photos and Pinterest inspiration, we will create a space that is just right for you!  We find the furniture and finishes and send you a list to purchase everything available online.</p>
          <p>The cost depends on the square footage of the space and your specific needs, but generally starts around $2,000 (not including the furniture and finishes cost).</p>
          <h5 class="black">Here's what we need from you:</h5>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li>- Photos of the space from different angles in daylight and in the evening</li>
              <li>- Dimensions of the room</li>
              <li>- Inspiration images(We LOVE Pintrest)</li>
              <li>- Your feedback</li>
          </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h5 class="img-desc">Updated Floor Plan</h5>
          <img src="/img/e-design/floor-plan.png" class="img-responsive padded-vertical" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 text">
          <h5 class="black">What you'll recieve:</h5>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li>- New floorplan</li>
              <li>- Mood board with furniture and finishes</li>
              <li>- A list of products online to furnish your space</li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="black">Step-by-step E-Design</h5>
          <ol>
              <li>Fill out our questionnaire.</li>
              <li>Take photos of the space from different angles with daylight and evening light.  The more the better!</li>
              <li>Measure the room and record the dimensions for us. Don’t forget to add in any windows, doors, fireplaces or strange angles.</li>
              <li>Go onto Pinterest and pin away anything that you love.  This could be a photo of rope or a color you are drawn to or just a room that you really like.</li>
              <li>Sit back and relax.  We are creating a special space just for you!</li>
              <li>Review our design to let us know what you think.  We will be sending you a floor plan and mood board with the products we think you will love.</li>
              <li>If it is not perfect, this is when we can make adjustments.</li>
              <li>Receive our final floor plan, mood board and purchasing list.</li>
              <li>Follow the purchase list as yor buying guide.  Then, re-create the floor plan that we’ve given you once your furniture has arrived.</li>
              <li>Have your friends over to show off your new space!</li>
          </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h5 class="img-desc">Furnished Floor Plan</h5>
          <img src="/img/e-design/living-room-rendering.png" class="img-responsive padded-vertical" />
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-lg questionaire" ng-click="toggleQForm()">Questionaire</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<global-modal show='qShow'>
    <h2 class="text-center">Questionaire</h2>
    <form id="signup" name="questioniareForm">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12">
                <h3 class="padded-vertical">Contact Details</h3>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="name">Name:</label>
                      <input type="text" name="name" ng-model="formData.name" class="form-control" required/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="email">Email:</label>
                      <input type="email" name="email" ng-model="formData.email" class="form-control" required/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="address">Address:</label>
                      <input type="text" name="address" ng-model="formData.address" class="form-control" required/>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="city">City:</label>
                      <input type="text" name="city" ng-model="formData.city" class="form-control" required/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="state">State:</label>
                      <select class="form-control" id="state" name="state" required>
                			<option value="">State</option>
                			<option value="AK">Alaska</option>
                			<option value="AL">Alabama</option>
                			<option value="AR">Arkansas</option>
                			<option value="AZ">Arizona</option>
                			<option value="CA">California</option>
                			<option value="CO">Colorado</option>
                			<option value="CT">Connecticut</option>
                			<option value="DC">District of Columbia</option>
                			<option value="DE">Delaware</option>
                			<option value="FL">Florida</option>
                			<option value="GA">Georgia</option>
                			<option value="HI">Hawaii</option>
                			<option value="IA">Iowa</option>
                			<option value="ID">Idaho</option>
                			<option value="IL">Illinois</option>
                			<option value="IN">Indiana</option>
                			<option value="KS">Kansas</option>
                			<option value="KY">Kentucky</option>
                			<option value="LA">Louisiana</option>
                			<option value="MA">Massachusetts</option>
                			<option value="MD">Maryland</option>
                			<option value="ME">Maine</option>
                			<option value="MI">Michigan</option>
                			<option value="MN">Minnesota</option>
                			<option value="MO">Missouri</option>
                			<option value="MS">Mississippi</option>
                			<option value="MT">Montana</option>
                			<option value="NC">North Carolina</option>
                			<option value="ND">North Dakota</option>
                			<option value="NE">Nebraska</option>
                			<option value="NH">New Hampshire</option>
                			<option value="NJ">New Jersey</option>
                			<option value="NM">New Mexico</option>
                			<option value="NV">Nevada</option>
                			<option value="NY">New York</option>
                			<option value="OH">Ohio</option>
                			<option value="OK">Oklahoma</option>
                			<option value="OR">Oregon</option>
                			<option value="PA">Pennsylvania</option>
                			<option value="PR">Puerto Rico</option>
                			<option value="RI">Rhode Island</option>
                			<option value="SC">South Carolina</option>
                			<option value="SD">South Dakota</option>
                			<option value="TN">Tennessee</option>
                			<option value="TX">Texas</option>
                			<option value="UT">Utah</option>
                			<option value="VA">Virginia</option>
                			<option value="VT">Vermont</option>
                			<option value="WA">Washington</option>
                			<option value="WI">Wisconsin</option>
                			<option value="WV">West Virginia</option>
                			<option value="WY">Wyoming</option>
                		</select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="name">Zip:</label>
                      <input type="number" name="zip" ng-model="formData.zip" class="form-control" required/>
                    </div>

                </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12">
                <h3 class="padded-vertical">Preferences/Style Details</h3>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="name">What rooms are you looking to e-design?</label>
                      <input type="text" name="rooms" ng-model="formData.rooms" class="form-control" required/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="budget">What is your overall budget, including design fees and furniture purchases?</label>
                      <input type="text" name="budget" ng-model="formData.budget" class="form-control" required/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="likes">What do you like and dislike about the space?</label>
                      <textarea name="likes" ng-model="formData.likes" class="form-control"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="space">How is the space going to be used? (i.e. to relax or entertain)</label>
                      <textarea name="space" ng-model="formData.space" class="form-control"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="users">Who will be the users of the space?</label>
                      <input type="text" name="users" ng-model="formData.users" class="form-control"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="keep">Are there specific items you would like to keep in the design?  If so, please provide photos.</label>
                      <input type="text" name="keep" ng-model="formData.keep" class="form-control"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6">
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="style">What colors and styles are you drawn to and want to see in the design?</label>
                      <textarea name="style" ng-model="formData.style" class="form-control"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="dislike">What colors and styles do you dislike?</label>
                      <textarea name="dislike" ng-model="formData.dislike" class="form-control"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Do you like patterns or solids?</label>
                        <div class="radio-inline">
                            <label><input type="radio" name="patterns" ng-model="formData.patterns" value="patterns" checked>Patterns</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="radio-inline">
                            <label><input type="radio" name="patterns" ng-model="formData.solids" value="solids">Solids</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="feel">What is the overall feeling that you’d like to have in the space?</label>
                      <textarea name="feel" ng-model="formData.feel" class="form-control"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label>Do you like the current lighting?</label>
                      <div class="radio-inline">
                          <label><input type="radio" name="lighting" value="yes" ng-model="formData.lightingYes" checked>Yes</label>
                      </div>
                      <div class="radio-inline">
                          <label><input type="radio" name="lighting" ng-model="formData.lightingNo" value="no">No</label>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="time">Is there a specific timeline that you have for the project?</label>
                      <input type="text" name="time" ng-model="formData.time" class="form-control" />
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="extra">Is there anything else you’d like us to know about regarding the design?</label>
                      <textarea name="extra" ng-model="formData.extra" class="form-control"></textarea>
                  </div>

                </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group pull-right">
          <input type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" ng-disabled="questioniareForm.$invalid" ng-click="submitQuestionaire()" value="Submit"/>
        </div>
    </form>
  </global-modal>

<section class="cta bg-black">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h3>The most beautiful thing we can create is the mysterious. It is the source of all true art and science.   -Albert Einstein</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
